"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/437355","Ministry of Defence","false","2015-12-15","<p>Territorial waters around the British Overseas Territories are monitored through a variety of means. The level of monitoring is commensurate with any potential threat.</p><br />","Portsmouth North","Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/437355/answer",,,,,,"2015-12-15T16:34:17.257Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/437355/answer","Biography information for Penny Mordaunt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/437355/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2015-12-11","British Overseas Territories: Territorial Waters","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what steps he is taking to monitor unauthorised entry into British territorial waters around British Overseas Territories.","false","Biography information for Craig Whittaker","Calder Valley","Craig Whittaker","19761"
